videos.headline: Jackson escapes Mississippi State's blitz
videos.description: Lamar Jackson somehow escapes the pressure and finds a hole for a 7-yard gain.

videos.headline: Williams finds end zone for quick Mississippi State TD
videos.description: Aeris Williams runs untouched for a 5-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Mississippi State TE injured after big gain
videos.description: Jordan Thomas gets the Bulldogs into Louisville territory after a 29-yard catch-and-run, but limps off the field after the play.

videos.headline: Jackson, Louisville score TD on 9-play drive
videos.description: Lamar Jackson throws a 5-yard strike to Charles Standberry, who just gets it across the goal line for a 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Thompson gets to the edge for huge gain
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson gets to the outside and runs through Louisville defenders for a 23-yard run.

videos.headline: Thompson takes big hit but gets Mississippi State TD
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson runs up the middle and gets to the end zone for a 14-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Smith tip-toes sideline for 35-yard catch-and-run
videos.description: Lamar Jackson hooks up with Jaylen Smith for a 35-yard catch while drawing a personal foul penalty against Mississippi State.

videos.headline: Jackson dazzles on TD run
videos.description: Lamar Jackson splits defenders on a 13-yard touchdown run to draw even with Mississippi State.

videos.headline: Official can't handle toss from Jackson
videos.description: Lamar Jackson tosses the ball to an official after the play is dead, but he can't complete the catch.

videos.headline: Mississippi State picks off Jackson
videos.description: Lamar Jackson misses his reciever and Mark McLaurin intercepts the pass after Jackson had thrown 114 straight passes without a pick.

videos.headline: Jackson throws second interception
videos.description: Cameron Dantzler picks off Lamar Jackson's pass and returns it 15 yards to Louisville's 37-yard line.

videos.headline: Louisville gets ball back on fumble recovery
videos.description: Trumaine Washington strips and recovers the football to give the ball right back to Louisville's offense.

videos.headline: Jackson scampers for 75-yard run
videos.description: Lamar Jackson breaks through a hole for a 75-yard gain to put the Cardinals in the red zone.

videos.headline: Jackson puts Louisville on top with second TD pass
videos.description: Lamar Jackson shovels a pass over the middle to Jaylen Smith for an 11-yard touchdown to put the Cardinals on top 21-17.

videos.headline: Petrino: 'Our players are really battling'
videos.description: Louisville coach Bobby Petrino is pleased with the big plays from the Cardinals' defense, but says his team has to "take care of the football."

videos.headline: Mississippi State muffs punt, Louisville recovers
videos.description: Gabe Myles mishandles the punt and Louisville recovers the ball at the 20-yard line.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Thompson throws interception
videos.description: Chucky Williams picks off Keytaon Thompson and gives Louisville's offense good field position.

videos.headline: Mississippi State picks off Jackson for third time
videos.description: Mark McLaurin intercepts Lamar Jackson for the second time today and returns it 12 yards.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Thompson's TD ties game
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson punches in a 2-yard touchdown to even the score at 24 in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Jackson hurdles defender for first down
videos.description: Lamar Jackson shows off his athleticism on this 4th-and-2 rush to the outside for a 7-yard gain.

videos.headline: Thompson's third rushing TD puts Mississippi State in front
videos.description: Keytaon Thompson keeps it himself for a 1-yard touchdown to give Mississippi State a 31-27 lead with less than four minutes remaining in the game.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's McLaurin gets third takeaway
videos.description: Mark McLaurin picks off Lamar Jackson late in the fourth quarter, Jackson's fourth turnover of the game.

videos.headline: Mississippi State celebrates way too early
videos.description: Mississippi State players dump a Gatorade bucket on Greg Knox before the game was actually over.

videos.headline: Knox: QB Thompson played up to his capabilities
videos.description: MSU interim coach Greg Knox talks about QB Keytaon Thompson's play and competing for four quarters in win vs. Louisville.

videos.headline: Mississippi State slows down Jackson, Louisville to win TaxSlayer Bowl
videos.description: Lamar Jackson throws a career-high four interceptions in Louisville's TaxSlayer Bowl loss to Mississippi State on Saturday.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Mississippi State slows down Jackson, Louisville to win TaxSlayer Bowl) 2017/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: McShay on Jackson: 'He's a difficult evaluation'
videos.description: Lamar Jackson been an electrifying quarterback for Louisville, but Todd McShay explains why he might need another year of development before declaring for the draft.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (McShay on Jackson: 'He's a difficult evaluation') 2017/12/30 ESHEET SVPSC
